{"tid":1696493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[出招］【何君堯遇襲】廖長江提休會待續　討論區選應對措施","createTime":"2019-11-06T08:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T08:26:29.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41e1bf8390d6c5466525e3ab8505f432d6f3e1b5","tid":1696493,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:00:29.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯今早在屯門擺設區議會選舉街站時遇襲。在下午的立法會大會上，建制派召集人廖長江提出休會待續議案，要求討論政府確保候選人安全及區選公平公正的應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n建制派召集人廖長江在大會提出休會待續議案，表示近日不斷發生區議會選舉競選活動受到暴力衝擊的事件，包括縱火、破壞候選人辦公室及滋擾競選活動，暴力程度不斷升級，有候選人被咬甩部份耳朵，有候選人被人用刀襲擊，認為大會要休會討論政府對候選人和競選團隊的人身安全，以及對確保區議會選舉公平、公開、公正進行的即時應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n廖長江今日下午在立法會大會上提出休會待續議案，指日不斷發生涉及區議會選舉競選活動受到暴力衝擊的事件，包括縱火、破壞候選人辦公室、破壞及滋擾競選活動，而且暴力程度不斷升級，有候選人被咬甩部份耳朵，有候選人今早被人用刀襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n他認為大會要討論政府對候選人和競選團隊的人身安全，以及對確保區議會選舉公平公開公正進行的即時應對措施。立法會主席梁君彥隨即宣布暫停會議處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%BB%96%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F%E6%8F%90%E4%BC%91%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%85%E7%BA%8C-%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E5%25BB%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%2585%25E7%25BA%258C-%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD%2F&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=8861e602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E5%25BB%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%2585%25E7%25BA%258C-%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD%2F&h=a91fedd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%BB%96%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F%E6%8F%90%E4%BC%91%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%85%E7%BA%8C-%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD/</a>"},{"pid":"cb4e02196c936cef20893b3dd2fd9f31a8714c5d","tid":1696493,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"11月9日：7區開花！香港人反抗！<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689356</a>"},{"pid":"096d9b44b981828a1d8a45858abdcba313562337","tid":1696493,"uid":47239,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"自編自導到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db031ea458889942117205feab7cb8b00c5a69fe","tid":1696493,"uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"人渣<br />\n民主派被人打唔見你衝出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b0066d9464c8519595f461f2f4300c08f071c2","tid":1696493,"uid":80560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"096d9b44b981828a1d8a45858abdcba313562337","tid":1696493,"uid":47239,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"自編自導到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"想借機會取消區議會選舉"},{"pid":"4c5ce10a1d4323d8265dcbb453ebb2b9940576af","tid":1696493,"uid":21757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"點解係何出時先噉做<br />\n如果最終延遲區選<br />\n好難唔相信今日呢場係自編自導"},{"pid":"4c55097f97b13504473b9e13adc0c08aef749690","tid":1696493,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}